<p>Big O is typeset as an italicized uppercase "<span class=3D"texhtml mvar=
" style=3D"font-style:italic;">O</span><span style=3D"padding-left:.15em;">=
"</span>, as in the following example: <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-=
math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-=
a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/M=
athML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyle O(n^{2})}">
