Greek-named Bachmann=E2=80=93Landau notations, it needs no special symbol. =
However, some authors use the calligraphic variant <span class=3D"mwe-math-=
element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-=
math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org=
